                        <interp inst="t18430821-name-573" type="given" value="WALTER RICHARD"></interp>WALTER RICHARD WATKINS</persName>
                  </hi>. I live in Bowl-square, Lower White Cross-street, and am a porter—on the afternoon of the 10th of August, I was going up Moorgate-street, and had a great coat and a wrapper inside my truck—a young man came, spoke, and I missed it—I went with him—the policeman had the prisoner in charge with it.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <persName id="t18430821-name-574" type="witnessName">
