                        <interp inst="t18430821-name-574" type="surname" value="HUGHES"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18430821-name-574" type="given" value="JAMES WILLIAM"></interp>JAMES WILLIAM HUGHES</persName>
                  </hi>. On the afternoon of the 10th of August, I was in Great Swan Alley which crosses London Wall—I saw the prisoner go behind the truck and abstract the coat—I told the prosecutor—I went round another way and caught him, with the coat on his arm—I gave him to the policeman, who came up almost as quick as myself.</p>
